Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大得不像話的傢伙是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.04,0:00:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露卡迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是剛才的那個怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬了勒庫托魯變化成那樣的姿態了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.42,0:01:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H4f807b&\fad(1000,0)}力量的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.96,0:01:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說被那個巨大的蚯蚓般的傢伙幹掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰被幹掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.89,0:02:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位都平安太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆  我擔心其他的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.23,0:02:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在停止攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在撤退  重整隊形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在那傢伙只是在準備下一發的琥珀金炮而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要它存在  逃到哪裡都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說不打倒它  我們就無路可逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  那樣的怪物要怎麼樣才能打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能封印梅露卡迪斯的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼  奧伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:03:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有神聖百詩篇集中的「力量的語言」有那個力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩篇集中有那樣的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳言大部分詩篇集都是用來振奮精靈駕馭梅露卡迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及讚頌神之偉業的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中只有一個咒歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「力量的語言」能夠壓制住梅露卡迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰能夠詠唱它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能夠詠唱的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為人類並繼承始祖之名的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏  知道咒歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀金炮要發射了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏  快詠唱咒歌「力量的語言」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要到達臨界點了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  詠唱「力量的語言」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白  不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你回想起咒歌之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來阻止那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的墮天之翼和我的艾德拉姆把它的琥珀金炮給擋回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的東西要怎麼擋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別多想了  相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓足勁了  阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  只是被吹了一下熱風而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再承受琥珀金的攻擊的話您的身體就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧伽姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都一副消極的臉孔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們以為我是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大魔王哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請相信我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精族將常伴你們左右
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  將所有的思念化作力量獻給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾撒魯  讓我看看第一戰士的骨氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是共患難的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會盡綿薄之力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你也要相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來吸引那傢伙的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為莉安瓏爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要發射了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須再次目睹那樣的景像嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明阿隆大人說了相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治癒魔法不管用  為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琥珀金造成的傷對阿隆大人來說是致命的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使用治癒魔法  那作用也是微乎其微的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明決定要保護大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連治療傷口都不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來  阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算就這樣再次沉睡千年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來  阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙腳不是為了站立而生的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了站著前往王道的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普依路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起建造阿努文吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏  讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  所以你什麼都不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的吧  我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己內在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案全部都在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了呢  莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得的  「力量的語言」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不使用你所繼承的普依路強大的妖精族力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「力量的語言」是無法使用的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主張就認為是不是因為這個力量讓我變得孤獨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也許已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家讓我注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白晝的太陽  新月的黑暗都在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪一個都是必須珍惜的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論獲得多麼強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:12:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓋爾族的莉安瓏這一點是不會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捨去一切觀念束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你作為你自己存在於這個世界的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界將以莉安瓏為中心運轉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的一切都將化作你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.28,0:12:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助大家  幫助阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏的話一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莉姆拉  看著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風  光  大海  天空  大地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切生物的鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Non  est  ad  astra  mollis  e  terris  via
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}大地通往明星的道路並不平穩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.05,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.27,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:27.85,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這就是咒歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是「力量的語言」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉安瓏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nutritur  vento,vento  restinguitur  ignis
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}火能被風吹旺  也能被風吹滅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dona  nobis  pacem
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}請給予我們和平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被區區的人類…完美的我被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我  絕對神瓦特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來  別過來  別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾撒魯  和他做個了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是最後了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被稱為新始之月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好適合一切都已結束的今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是寧靜的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普依路  結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是他的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是一起行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成長為一個堅強的男人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有必須去開拓的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也請你繼續指引必須承擔起這一切的阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來還有得辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就授予他古老的阿魯比昂王國的妖精王的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Pendragon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你授予給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  阿隆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.32,0:17:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日此時授予阿爾撒魯古老的阿魯比昂王國的王太子的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承龍之王  成為統治這一片土地的王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之王  阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以勇猛的力量與善良的內心取回這個世界的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願黎明之星的加護永遠守護您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得如此偉大了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著妖精之冠的人類的王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯比昂國王復活了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們見證了嶄新開始的瞬間了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾撒魯也終於成為王了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是王冠什麼的可是妨礙狩獵的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確一點也不合適
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在就算是說謊也說聲合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮廷樂師千萬別忘了我塔列辛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我為這次戴冠式增添點色彩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你  阿爾撒魯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獻給雷吉亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往阿努文的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一起前進吧  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了這場大戰  阿瓦隆誕生了新的國王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將這一年定為阿魯比昂復活歷元年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立了新王國
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情享受著活在這世上的快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大國王和小國王合力建立了新王國
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  之後的事該怎麼寫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就先和大家討論一下如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家討論？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能寫很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  劍是用來貫徹自己的信念的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  一定要成為能保護朋友的身後的堅強的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞  去狩獵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧塔維亞去狩獵…喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要去狩獵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然突然飛撲到我懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就那麼想見我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  放下我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不用害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我蹭我蹭～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔列辛大人  您在這裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計是肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就給你做吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是寵愛它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是按照預言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承布利岡蒂斯的族長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會觸碰到眾神的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為野獸的食料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食料…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說一輩子都要被使喚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  蘇伊露
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被牛小姐當笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:22:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然是不幸的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你吧  打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛打造好的金幣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建國紀念金幣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片土地之上  龍族翱翔天際
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.44,0:22:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨人跫音震地  妖精高歌吟唱  人類鼓舞歡欣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想還未到來的王國  阿努文的卡艾魯{\bold0}·{\r}米爾丁在此長眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今後的漫長道路的盡頭  我們也將在此安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願總有一天能夠再次相會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.41,0:22:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像過去一樣並肩戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.58,0:22:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這片無涯的大海  無盡的大地見證  我們祈願著…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望實現了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:22:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得復活的劍啊  這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  估計用不上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.08,0:23:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  因為在阿隆大人的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.30,0:23:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿隆大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.56,0:23:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起艾德拉姆  現在還是你織的圍巾溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明星大人  感謝您的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:12.85,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胸に届いた声は　熱く焦がれてゆくけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:26.66,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いたみは懐かしく　なぜ心地よいのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:41.68,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まどろみのなか　待ち続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:21:00.01,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彷徨う世界に　見つけたものは　soul
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:12.36,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ancient  memory　時を越えて　dream  of  earth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:27.75,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風のささやき　花はゆらめき　こたえあう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:41.12,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全てのものに　時を越えて　heart  of  earth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:22:03.12,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星の導き　君は未来の　旅人となるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:46.98,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}暗闇の中　あきらめてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:23:05.19,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}差し出すその手に　見つけたものは　love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.89,0:23:18.61,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ancient  memory　時を越えて　heart  of  earth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:41.94,injp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星の導き　君は未来の　夢となるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:12.85,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傳入心中的言語　如此炙熱　好似烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:26.66,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}令人懷念的傷痛　心中迴盪　如此舒暢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:41.68,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}縱使身處混沌　卻依然在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.66,0:21:00.01,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彷徨的世界中　覓得一絲深意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:12.36,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悠久之憶　穿越時空　描繪大地之夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:27.75,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}微風細雨　花瓣輕輕灑落
